quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"S yitri mara ixeppi!"
  53,2,"Ur innetlaf, ur i$liv umeddakwel nnwen."
  53,3,"Ur d iqqaô akken i s ihwan."
  53,4,"D aweêêi kan, id ippuweêêan."
  53,5,"Islemd it bab n tezmert iqwan."
  53,6,"D bab n tezmert irs ed"
  53,7,"u neppa di lejba aâlayen."
  53,8,"Sinna iqeôb ed, ippucengel,"
  53,9,"atan tasurift n sin ixtucen, ne$ ur tebbwiv."
  53,10,"D$a iweêêa i umdan iS, ayen iweêêa."
  53,11,"Ur iskaddeb wul deg wayen iwala."
  53,12,"Day a t tnaqwmem, $ef wayen iwala?"
  53,13,"Ni$ iéôa t di trusi s nniven,"
  53,14,"ar tedxwent n talast,"
  53,15,"u$uô illa leonan usemlili."
  53,16,"Mi tesbur tedxwent ta$wlaft,"
  53,17,"ur iwweônenni yiéôi, ur izgir."
  53,18,"Ni$ iwala kra issekniyen imeqwôaêanen, n Mass is."
  53,19,"Twalam Allat akked Lâuzza?"
  53,20,"Akked Manat, tis krav nniven?"
  53,21,"Day i kunwi ddkeô, i Neppa nnta?"
  53,22,"Wagi, ihi, d beîîu aneêyaf."
  53,23,"Wigi d ismawen kan i sent tefkam, kunwi akked imezwura nnwen. Ur sent d Issers Öebbi kra udabu. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya, akked wayen cehwant teôwiêin. Ni$ tusa ten id nnhaya s$uô Mass nnsen."
  53,24,"Aâni, i umdan, ayen issaram?"
  53,25,"Tamezwarut akked tneggarut, n Öebbi."
  53,26,"Acêal n lmalayek deg igenwan, ur d teppawi acemma ccafuâa nnsent, siwa deffir tsriê n Öebbi, $ef win Ib$a u Iôuva."
  53,27,"Ih, wid ur numin ara di laxeôt, ppaken i lmalayek ismawen n nnta."
  53,28,"Ur sâin fellas kra n tmusni. Ïîafaôen kan nnwaya. Wanag nnwaya ur tebbwi acemma si tidep."
  53,29,"Ihi, eoo win iwexxôen i usmekti nne£, i ib$an kan tudert n ddunit."
  53,30,"D aya ay sen tefka tmusni. Mass ik, war ccekk, Iéôa sennig akw, anwa innetlafen seg ubrid iS; Iéôa sennig akw, anwa i ipwanhan."
  53,31,"N Öebbi ayen akw illan deg igenwan, illan di tmurt. Ad Iqeîîi wid ifalîan $ef wayen xedmen, ad Ioazi wid issweqmen, s ûûam."
  53,32,"Wid ijunben ibekkaven ibararen akked tucmitin, siwa lfalîat fessusen, ihi, d uwsiâ ssmaê n Mass ik. Neppa Issen ikwen sennig akw, mi kwen id Ixleq seg wakal, mi tellam d icelleqluqen, deg iâabbav n tyimmatin nnwen. Ur staâmilet tezdeg deg iman nnwen! Neppa Iéôa sennig akw, anwa iêezzben."
  53,33,"Twalav win iwexxôen,"
  53,34,"i ifkan cwiî, iccuêen?"
  53,35,"Day isâa tamusni n tbavnit, d$a iwala?"
  53,36,"Ne$ ur ippuxebbeô $ef tewôiqin n Musa?"
  53,37,"Akked Ibôahim ineûêen?"
  53,38,"Ur ipbibbi yiwen taâkkwemt n wayev."
  53,39,"I umdan, siwa ayen inki."
  53,40,"Ankay is a t iwali."
  53,41,"Sinna, a t Ikafi s lufa."
  53,42,"Ih, ar Mass ik, taggara."
  53,43,"D Neppa i Issevûan, i Issruyen."
  53,44,"D Neppa i Ineqqen, i Issidiren."
  53,45,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tayuga, ddkeô akked nnta,"
  53,46,"Si tiqqit n l$ella ma tuzzel."
  53,47,"FellaS, axlaq nniven."
  53,48,"D Neppa i I$ennun, i Iqenâan."
  53,49,"D Neppa i d Mass n Ciâra."
  53,50,"D Neppa i Isnegren Âad imezwura."
  53,51,"Si Tamud, ur d Iooi ara."
  53,52,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, war ccekk, iugar iten ddens, lbbwe$v."
  53,53,"Issenger tid inneqlaben;"
  53,54,"Idel iten s wayen idellen."
  53,55,"Anta talalt n Mass ik ara tnamerev?"
  53,56,"Wagi d aneddaô seg ineddaôen n zik."
  53,57,"A d taéé tin d ippaééen."
  53,58,"War Öebbi, ur illi ara p id issdehôen."
  53,59,"Iswehm ikwen wawal a?"
  53,60,"La tdessem ur la tepprum!"
  53,61,"Kunwi di zzhu."
  53,62,"Knut i Öebbi, âabdet."
